		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">Exposure to your fungal spores has granted you and your companions a new method of communication. You gain telepathy out to a range of 30 feet. If you already have telepathy from another feature, extend its range by 30 feet.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Additionally, once per long rest you may choose a number of willing creatures equal to your proficiency bonus to share in your telepathic abilities. The chosen creatures must have an Intelligence score of 3 or higher, though you do not need to share a language to communicate in this way. You and the chosen creatures are able to telepathically communicate with one another for the next hour so long as they remain within 30 feet of you.</p>",
